	<h1 class="title">专访伊藤穰一：投资人如何管理麻省理工媒体实验室？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/14/small/14.jpg?1399504790" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐涛</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-05-28 10:35:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/884/medium/884.jpg?1436637614" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


